"{\"uid\": \"breitbart.com-europe-2024-04-24-french-police-clear-migrant-camps-out-of-paris-in-alleged-pre-olympics-clean\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AP) - French police evicted migrants from a makeshift camp in Paris a few steps away from the Seine River on Tuesday, the latest operation in what aid groups call a campaign of '\\u00b4social cleansing\\\" ahead of the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 233, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9251547860341043, \"rank\": 0.0808948424858829, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3865884493473775e-31, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before dawn on an unusually cold April morning, around 30 teenage boys and young men from West Africa were awakened by police and urged to pack their tents and belongings.\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999088078143863, \"rank\": 9.119766566061539e-05, \"text\": \"West Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of them were underage and in the process of seeking residency papers.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was already scared but I am even more scared because I don\\u00b4t know where to go,\\\" said Boubacar Traore, 16, who said he fled conflict in Burkina Faso and arrived in France two months ago.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 571, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999999946730895, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boubacar Traore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"score\": 0.9999999590640991, \"rank\": 4.093589693898894e-08, \"text\": \"Burkina Faso\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\"}, {\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9983211160985426, \"rank\": 0.0008550511788362329, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The operation came days after police carried out a large-scale eviction at France\\u00b4s biggest squatter camp in a suburb south of Paris.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police officers check a migrant in a makeshift camp, early Tuesday, April 23, 2024 in Paris.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French police officers have evicted migrants from a makeshift camp in Paris a few steps away from the Seine River, as similar operations have been carried out by authorities ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1097, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3865884493473775e-31, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(AP Photo/Nicolas Garriga)  A police officers checks a migrant's tent in a makeshift camp, early Tuesday, April 23, 2024 in Paris.\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9251547860341043, \"rank\": 0.0808948424858829, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French police officers have evicted migrants from a makeshift camp in Paris a few steps away from the Seine River, as similar operations have been carried out by authorities ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.3865884493473775e-31, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(AP Photo/Nicolas Garriga)  Such evictions and evacuations of migrant tent camps happen every spring after the end of a winter '\\u00b4truce\\\" during which authorities put such actions on hold.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9251547860341043, \"rank\": 0.0808948424858829, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But aid groups working with migrants and other vulnerable people in the Paris region say these efforts are intensifying ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They note that people are being sent far away from the capital instead of being offered shelter in the Paris region, where many asylum-seekers have upcoming court dates.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The authorities want to have a clean place for the Olympics Games.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They don\\u00b4t want the tourists to see Paris as a city full of migrants and asylum seekers,\\\" Elias Hufganel, a volunteer with a group serving refugees and immigrants, said at the Paris tent camp Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris police said the operation was carried out for security reasons, notably because the tent camp was near schools.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a nearby street stood two large buses heading to Besan\\u00e7on, 400 kilometers (240 miles) southeast of Paris.\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2369, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\", \"score\": 0.9970925063704774, \"rank\": 0.001406544726641828, \"text\": \"Besan\\u00e7on\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\"}, {\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities proposed to relocate the young men there and offered them housing for three weeks.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But most didn\\u00b4t want to take up that offer, fearing being even more isolated and with no plan after the three weeks run out.\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traore was among those who refused to travel because he is awaiting a court date in Paris in two days.\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2731, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994104201, \"rank\": 5.895591945450554e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unclear where he would sleep Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pleaselet us knowif you are having issues with commenting.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025 Breitbart\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2889, \"end\": 2898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"score\": 0.9999987735062196, \"rank\": 1.2264952475524733e-06, \"text\": \"Breitbart\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breitbart_News\"}]}]}"